{"tid":904823,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【90後男女健康研討會】歡迎東區友 運動友 吹水友","createTime":"2018-11-16T16:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T09:10:26.000Z","uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb791b12a334b29c62aac1b1fdebf0de955fffce","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"本谷無其他要求，唯獨三樣野唔做得 狗公 撩是鬥非 潛水 必踢 唔會另行通知<br />\n<br />\n谷主只有一個要求，無論各位是否單身或是有伴侶，希望都可以認識到更多朋友<br />\n從而多一個機會走入人地既一生<br />\n<br />\n只要你想入谷主都無任歡迎，各位巴打絲打唔好諗LA，<br />\n有興趣想識朋友又鐘意有活動的人，快D加入我地<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節將會有活動，希望見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣既，快啲填表啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeR0_1fZObFW_JZp9_wmQtVFe_jW6Vya5GepB6G9ps3GJS4ww/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeR0_1fZObFW_JZp9_wmQtVFe_jW6Vya5GepB6G9ps3GJS4ww%2Fviewform&d=w85OPF0jygj%2F2z1%2BvXTwmaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7770dba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeR0_1fZObFW_JZp9_wmQtVFe_jW6Vya5GepB6G9ps3GJS4ww/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"853d12540efede3b2979384291bb8c9f34375e32","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10d9eb9cfeba66f89ab4250b8f44440830b42335","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3a465662cf3afd486229a68420626a59656db29","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T23:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff79dd386f3fbab7af4f2afa497c3a58978ba962","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:30:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cc0688dc66388bb414e34e6a378c75ea39a40506","tid":904823,"uid":60489,"like":0,"dislike